{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1401,"text":"Fifty-four percent of the world's population"},{"time":4955,"text":"lives in our cities."},{"time":7536,"text":"In developing countries,"},{"time":9181,"text":"one third of that population"},{"time":11461,"text":"is living in slums."},{"time":14408,"text":"Seventy-five percent of global energy consumption"},{"time":19040,"text":"occurs in our cities,"},{"time":22090,"text":"and 80 percent of gas emissions"},{"time":24599,"text":"that cause global warming"},{"time":26354,"text":"come from our cities."},{"time":29392,"text":"So things that you and I might think about"},{"time":32417,"text":"as global problems,"},{"time":34532,"text":"like climate change, the energy crisis"},{"time":37180,"text":"or poverty,"},{"time":38842,"text":"are really, in many ways, city problems."},{"time":43702,"text":"They will not be solved"},{"time":45564,"text":"unless people who live in cities,"},{"time":48582,"text":"like most of us,"},{"time":50501,"text":"actually start doing a better job,"},{"time":53293,"text":"because right now, we are \nnot doing a very good one."},{"time":57249,"text":"And that becomes very clear"},{"time":60585,"text":"when we look into three aspects of city life:"},{"time":64479,"text":"first, our citizens' willingness to engage"},{"time":68605,"text":"with democratic institutions;"},{"time":71417,"text":"second, our cities' ability to really include"},{"time":76221,"text":"all of their residents;"},{"time":78763,"text":"and lastly, our own ability"},{"time":81940,"text":"to live fulfilling and happy lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86405,"text":"When it comes to engagement,"},{"time":88184,"text":"the data is very clear."},{"time":91114,"text":"Voter turnout around the world"},{"time":93195,"text":"peaked in the late '80s,"},{"time":95636,"text":"and it has been declining at a pace"},{"time":97481,"text":"that we have never seen before,"},{"time":100543,"text":"and if those numbers are bad at the national level,"},{"time":104138,"text":"at the level of our cities,"},{"time":106147,"text":"they are just dismal."},{"time":109236,"text":"In the last two years,"},{"time":110830,"text":"two of the world's most consolidated,"},{"time":113331,"text":"oldest democracies, the U.S. and France,"},{"time":117166,"text":"held nationwide municipal elections."},{"time":120971,"text":"In France, voter turnout hit a record low."},{"time":124871,"text":"Almost 40 percent of voters decided"},{"time":128933,"text":"not to show up."},{"time":131621,"text":"In the U.S., the numbers were even scarier."},{"time":134710,"text":"In some American cities,"},{"time":136987,"text":"voter turnout was close to five percent."},{"time":141981,"text":"I'll let that sink in for a second."},{"time":143770,"text":"We're talking about democratic cities"},{"time":146188,"text":"in which 95 percent of people"},{"time":149563,"text":"decided that it was not important"},{"time":151981,"text":"to elect their leaders."},{"time":154726,"text":"The city of L.A., a city of four million people,"},{"time":158380,"text":"elected its mayor with just a bit over 200,000 votes."},{"time":163309,"text":"That was the lowest turnout the city had seen"},{"time":165795,"text":"in 100 years."},{"time":168676,"text":"Right here, in my city of Rio,"},{"time":171720,"text":"in spite of mandatory voting,"},{"time":174794,"text":"almost 30 percent of the voting population"},{"time":178292,"text":"chose to either annul their votes"},{"time":180857,"text":"or stay home and pay a fine"},{"time":183489,"text":"in the last mayoral elections."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186820,"text":"When it comes to inclusiveness,"},{"time":189139,"text":"our cities are not the best cases of success either,"},{"time":192244,"text":"and again, you don't need to look very far"},{"time":195134,"text":"in order to find proof of that."},{"time":196889,"text":"The city of Rio is incredibly unequal."},{"time":201388,"text":"This is Leblon."},{"time":203357,"text":"Leblon is the city's richest neighborhood."},{"time":206461,"text":"And this is Complexo do Alemão."},{"time":208900,"text":"This is where over 70,000"},{"time":211164,"text":"of the city's poorest residents live."},{"time":214415,"text":"Leblon has an HDI, a Human Development Index,"},{"time":218001,"text":"of .967."},{"time":221390,"text":"That is higher than Norway, Switzerland"},{"time":225211,"text":"or Sweden."},{"time":227452,"text":"Complexo do Alemão has an HDI of .711."},{"time":231181,"text":"It sits somewhere in between the HDI"},{"time":234111,"text":"of Algeria and Gabon."},{"time":237328,"text":"So Rio, like so many cities across the global South,"},{"time":242109,"text":"is a place where you can go from northern Europe"},{"time":245080,"text":"to sub-Saharan Africa"},{"time":246980,"text":"in the space of 30 minutes."},{"time":249984,"text":"If you drive, that is."},{"time":251693,"text":"If you take public transit, it's about two hours."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256440,"text":"And lastly, perhaps most importantly,"},{"time":260299,"text":"cities, with the incredible wealth"},{"time":262780,"text":"of relations that they enable,"},{"time":265282,"text":"could be the ideal places for human happiness"},{"time":269160,"text":"to flourish."},{"time":270562,"text":"We like being around people."},{"time":272987,"text":"We are social animals."},{"time":275383,"text":"Instead, countries where urbanization"},{"time":278006,"text":"has already peaked seem to be the very countries"},{"time":282228,"text":"in which cities have stopped making us happy."},{"time":286880,"text":"The United States population has suffered"},{"time":289484,"text":"from a general decrease in happiness"},{"time":292464,"text":"for the past three decades,"},{"time":295666,"text":"and the main reason is this."},{"time":298640,"text":"The American way of building cities"},{"time":301542,"text":"has caused good quality public spaces"},{"time":304253,"text":"to virtually disappear in many,"},{"time":306237,"text":"many American cities,"},{"time":307992,"text":"and as a result, they have seen"},{"time":309989,"text":"a decline of relations,"},{"time":312544,"text":"of the things that make us happy."},{"time":314748,"text":"Many studies show an increase"},{"time":316795,"text":"in solitude and a decrease in solidarity,"},{"time":321486,"text":"honesty, and social and civic participation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326142,"text":"So how do we start building cities"},{"time":329506,"text":"that make us care?"},{"time":332116,"text":"Cities that value their most important asset:"},{"time":336750,"text":"the incredible diversity"},{"time":339349,"text":"of the people who live in them?"},{"time":341555,"text":"Cities that make us happy?"},{"time":345212,"text":"Well, I believe that if we want to change"},{"time":347719,"text":"what our cities look like,"},{"time":350271,"text":"then we really have to change"},{"time":352961,"text":"the decision-making processes"},{"time":355504,"text":"that have given us the results \nthat we have right now."},{"time":359328,"text":"We need a participation revolution,"},{"time":362500,"text":"and we need it fast."},{"time":365374,"text":"The idea of voting as our \nonly exercise in citizenship"},{"time":370712,"text":"does not make sense anymore."},{"time":373670,"text":"People are tired of only being treated"},{"time":376199,"text":"as empowered individuals every few years"},{"time":380372,"text":"when it's time to delegate that power"},{"time":383522,"text":"to someone else."},{"time":385897,"text":"If the protests that swept Brazil"},{"time":388842,"text":"in June 2013 have taught us anything,"},{"time":393814,"text":"it's that every time we try"},{"time":396649,"text":"to exercise our power"},{"time":399101,"text":"outside of an electoral context,"},{"time":401958,"text":"we are beaten up, humiliated or arrested."},{"time":407212,"text":"And this needs to change,"},{"time":410419,"text":"because when it does,"},{"time":412633,"text":"not only will people re-engage"},{"time":414894,"text":"with the structures of representation,"},{"time":417380,"text":"but also complement these structures"},{"time":420654,"text":"with direct, effective, and \ncollective decision making,"},{"time":427572,"text":"decision making of the kind"},{"time":429496,"text":"that attacks inequality"},{"time":431542,"text":"by its very inclusive nature,"},{"time":434782,"text":"decision making of the kind"},{"time":436605,"text":"that can change our cities"},{"time":438821,"text":"into better places for us to live."}]},{"cues":[{"time":441937,"text":"But there is a catch, obviously:"},{"time":445416,"text":"Enabling widespread participation"},{"time":448157,"text":"and redistributing power"},{"time":450115,"text":"can be a logistical nightmare,"},{"time":452840,"text":"and there's where technology can play"},{"time":455129,"text":"an incredibly helpful role,"},{"time":457306,"text":"by making it easier for people to organize,"},{"time":460388,"text":"communicate and make decisions"},{"time":462452,"text":"without having to be in the same room"},{"time":464690,"text":"at the same time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466952,"text":"Unfortunately for us,"},{"time":468853,"text":"when it comes to fostering democratic processes,"},{"time":471879,"text":"our city governments have not used technology"},{"time":474964,"text":"to its full potential."},{"time":477942,"text":"So far, most city governments have been effective"},{"time":481159,"text":"at using tech to turn citizens into human sensors"},{"time":485742,"text":"who serve authorities with data on the city:"},{"time":489450,"text":"potholes, fallen trees or broken lamps."},{"time":493456,"text":"They have also, to a lesser extent,"},{"time":495886,"text":"invited people to participate in improving"},{"time":499486,"text":"the outcome of decisions"},{"time":501100,"text":"that were already made for them,"},{"time":504412,"text":"just like my mom when I was eight"},{"time":505987,"text":"and she told me that I had a choice:"},{"time":507753,"text":"I had to be in bed by 8 p.m.,"},{"time":509330,"text":"but I could choose my pink\npajamas or my blue pajamas."},{"time":513243,"text":"That's not participation,"},{"time":515482,"text":"and in fact, governments have not been very good"},{"time":519227,"text":"at using technology to enable participation"},{"time":522130,"text":"on what matters —"},{"time":524080,"text":"the way we allocate our budget,"},{"time":526393,"text":"the way we occupy our land,"},{"time":528615,"text":"and the way we manage our natural resources."},{"time":532164,"text":"Those are the kinds of decisions"},{"time":534278,"text":"that can actually impact global problems"},{"time":537158,"text":"that manifest themselves in our cities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":540980,"text":"The good news is,"},{"time":542506,"text":"and I do have good news to share with you,"},{"time":544369,"text":"we don't need to wait for governments to do this."},{"time":548666,"text":"I have reason to believe"},{"time":550636,"text":"that it's possible for citizens to build"},{"time":553224,"text":"their own structures of participation."},{"time":557757,"text":"Three years ago, I cofounded an organization"},{"time":560558,"text":"called Meu Rio,"},{"time":563045,"text":"and we make it easier for people in the city of Rio"},{"time":566125,"text":"to organize around causes and places"},{"time":569704,"text":"that they care about in their own city,"},{"time":572301,"text":"and have an impact on those causes and places"},{"time":574990,"text":"every day."},{"time":577318,"text":"In these past three years, Meu Rio grew"},{"time":580060,"text":"to a network of 160,000 citizens of Rio."},{"time":585928,"text":"About 40 percent of those \nmembers are young people"},{"time":589833,"text":"aged 20 to 29."},{"time":592072,"text":"That is one in every 15 young people"},{"time":596996,"text":"of that age in Rio today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":600828,"text":"Amongst our members is this adorable little girl,"},{"time":604460,"text":"Bia, to your right,"},{"time":606509,"text":"and Bia was just 11 years old"},{"time":609636,"text":"when she started a campaign using one of our tools"},{"time":612572,"text":"to save her model public school from demolition."},{"time":616161,"text":"Her school actually ranks among the best"},{"time":618253,"text":"public schools in the country,"},{"time":620525,"text":"and it was going to be demolished"},{"time":622257,"text":"by the Rio de Janeiro state government"},{"time":624811,"text":"to build, I kid you not,"},{"time":626701,"text":"a parking lot for the World Cup"},{"time":629524,"text":"right before the event happened."},{"time":631870,"text":"Bia started a campaign, and we even watched"},{"time":634364,"text":"her school 24/7 through webcam monitoring,"},{"time":637747,"text":"and many months afterwards,"},{"time":639761,"text":"the government changed their minds."},{"time":641392,"text":"Bia's school stayed in place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":644316,"text":"There's also Jovita."},{"time":646487,"text":"She's an amazing woman whose daughter"},{"time":648759,"text":"went missing about 10 years ago,"},{"time":651420,"text":"and since then, she has been looking"},{"time":653855,"text":"for her daughter."},{"time":655039,"text":"In that process, she found out"},{"time":657815,"text":"that first, she was not alone."},{"time":660368,"text":"In the last year alone, 2013,"},{"time":662956,"text":"6,000 people disappeared"},{"time":664830,"text":"in the state of Rio."},{"time":666706,"text":"But she also found out that in spite of that,"},{"time":669334,"text":"Rio had no centralized intelligence system"},{"time":673285,"text":"for solving missing persons cases."},{"time":676590,"text":"In other Brazilian cities, those systems"},{"time":679160,"text":"have helped solve up to 80 percent"},{"time":681550,"text":"of missing persons cases."},{"time":683586,"text":"She started a campaign,"},{"time":685329,"text":"and after the secretary of \nsecurity got 16,000 emails"},{"time":689311,"text":"from people asking him to do this,"},{"time":692124,"text":"he responded, and started to build a police unit"},{"time":695106,"text":"specializing in those cases."},{"time":696930,"text":"It was open to the public at the end of last month,"},{"time":700286,"text":"and Jovita was there"},{"time":702137,"text":"giving interviews and being very fancy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":705161,"text":"And then, there is Leandro."},{"time":707000,"text":"Leandro is an amazing guy"},{"time":708723,"text":"in a slum in Rio,"},{"time":710639,"text":"and he created a recycling project in the slum."},{"time":714062,"text":"At the end of last year, December 16,"},{"time":716512,"text":"he received an eviction order"},{"time":718604,"text":"by the Rio de Janeiro state government"},{"time":720584,"text":"giving him two weeks to leave the space"},{"time":724504,"text":"that he had been using for two years."},{"time":728244,"text":"The plan was to hand it over to a developer,"},{"time":730809,"text":"who planned to turn it into a construction site."},{"time":734229,"text":"Leandro started a campaign using one of our tools,"},{"time":737297,"text":"the Pressure Cooker,"},{"time":738875,"text":"the same one that Bia and Jovita used,"},{"time":741214,"text":"and the state government changed their minds"},{"time":744270,"text":"before Christmas Eve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":747536,"text":"These stories make me happy,"},{"time":750608,"text":"but not just because they have happy endings."},{"time":753655,"text":"They make me happy because they are"},{"time":756401,"text":"happy beginnings."},{"time":759100,"text":"The teacher and parent community at Bia's school"},{"time":761519,"text":"is looking for other ways they could improve"},{"time":763475,"text":"that space even further."},{"time":766952,"text":"Leandro has ambitious plans"},{"time":768663,"text":"to take his model to other\nlow-income communities in Rio,"},{"time":771616,"text":"and Jovita is volunteering at the police unit"},{"time":774827,"text":"that she helped created."},{"time":777667,"text":"Bia, Jovita and Leandro"},{"time":780415,"text":"are living examples of something"},{"time":782475,"text":"that citizens and city \ngovernments around the world"},{"time":786057,"text":"need to know:"},{"time":788461,"text":"We are ready."},{"time":791788,"text":"As citizens, we are ready"},{"time":794716,"text":"to decide on our common destinies,"},{"time":798271,"text":"because we know that the way we distribute power"},{"time":802290,"text":"says a lot about how we actually value everyone,"},{"time":807130,"text":"and because we know"},{"time":809360,"text":"that enabling and participating in local politics"},{"time":812855,"text":"is a sign that we truly care"},{"time":814978,"text":"about our relations to one another,"},{"time":817168,"text":"and we are ready to do this"},{"time":818890,"text":"in cities around the world right now."},{"time":822907,"text":"With the Our Cities network,"},{"time":825303,"text":"the Meu Rio team"},{"time":826640,"text":"hopes to share what we have learned"},{"time":828666,"text":"with other people who want to create"},{"time":830622,"text":"similar initiatives in their own cities."},{"time":833884,"text":"We have already started doing it in São Paulo"},{"time":836441,"text":"with incredible results,"},{"time":838137,"text":"and want to take it to cities around the world"},{"time":841444,"text":"through a network of citizen-centric,"},{"time":844369,"text":"citizen-led organizations"},{"time":846746,"text":"that can inspire us,"},{"time":848932,"text":"challenge us, and remind us to demand"},{"time":852396,"text":"real participation in our city lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":857447,"text":"It is up to us"},{"time":859409,"text":"to decide whether we want schools"},{"time":861894,"text":"or parking lots,"},{"time":864180,"text":"community-driven recycling projects"},{"time":866513,"text":"or construction sites,"},{"time":869116,"text":"loneliness or solidarity, cars or buses,"},{"time":871536,"text":"and it is our responsibility to do that now,"},{"time":875235,"text":"for ourselves, for our families,"},{"time":878659,"text":"for the people who make our lives worth living,"},{"time":882753,"text":"and for the incredible creativity,"},{"time":885620,"text":"beauty, and wonder that make our cities,"},{"time":889027,"text":"in spite of all of their problems,"},{"time":891614,"text":"the greatest invention of our time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":895330,"text":"Obrigado. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":897810,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}